00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:07,455
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa saat kau 9 tahun?</i></font>

531
00:40:10,124 --> 00:40:12,326
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu cuma kecelakaan saja.</font>

532
00:40:12,727 --> 00:40:14,228
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku yakin, pasti kejadian itu...</i></font>

533
00:40:14,562 --> 00:40:17,165
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...tak tertahankan bagimu.</i></font>

534
00:40:17,965 --> 00:40:20,735
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang mengada-ada
cerita itu buatmu?</font>

535
00:40:21,369 --> 00:40:23,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak menarik, lagi.</font>

536
00:40:23,538 --> 00:40:24,839
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Malah membosankan.</i></font>

537
00:40:25,706 --> 00:40:26,741
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kim Yong Chul.</i></font>

538
00:40:27,809 --> 00:40:29,243
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau bukan hanya...</i></font>

539
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:31,879
<font color=#FFFF00>...pembunuh berantai terkenal bagiku.</font>

540
00:40:33,414 --> 00:40:34,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau itu Reaper.</font>

541
00:40:35,817 --> 00:40:37,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa menjanjikan ini padamu.</font>

542
00:40:38,953 --> 00:40:40,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami akan belajar
mencermati cara kerjamu.</font>

543
00:40:40,888 --> 00:40:42,757
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kami tidak akan mengabaikanmu.</i></font>

544
00:40:44,959 --> 00:40:46,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau jadi
berpura-pura lemah begitu?</font>

545
00:40:47,295 --> 00:40:48,796
<font color=#FFFF00>Padahal ini baru permulaan.</font>

546
00:40:56,370 --> 00:40:57,905
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kumohon, Kim Yong Chul.</i></font>

547
00:40:59,474 --> 00:41:01,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertimbangkanlah sekali lagi.</font>

548
00:41:02,210 --> 00:41:03,377
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bagaimana?</i></font>

549
00:41:04,645 --> 00:41:05,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baru paham sekarang?</font>

550
00:41:07,215 --> 00:41:11,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau perlahan menyadari apa
ketakutan sejati itu?</font>

551
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:15,456
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau sesungguhnya tidak pernah
menjalani kehidupan yang layak.</i></font>

552
00:41:16,557 --> 00:41:18,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang yang kau cintai,
rumah dan keluarga...,</font>

553
00:41:20,595 --> 00:41:22,230
<font color=#FFFF00>...senyum bahagia...</font>

554
00:41:23,464 --> 00:41:24,932
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Makanya itu...</i></font>

555
00:41:25,766 --> 00:41:28,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin merampas semua yang
kausebutkan itu darimu.</font>

556
00:41:29,704 --> 00:41:31,672
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa? Tak boleh?</i></font>

557
00:41:37,278 --> 00:41:39,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, siapa ini yang datang?</font>

558
00:41:42,717 --> 00:41:44,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Senyum Hae Won manis juga.</font>

559
00:41:47,655 --> 00:41:49,323
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aroma tubuhnya juga pasti manis.</i></font>

560
00:41:50,491 --> 00:41:52,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi mana anak lelaki
tampan itu?</font>

561
00:42:01,502 --> 00:42:02,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu dia.</font>

562
00:42:04,839 --> 00:42:06,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tunggu, tunggu.</i></font>

563
00:42:08,676 --> 00:42:09,844
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ya, Ny. Seo.</i></font>

564
00:42:10,278 --> 00:42:12,313
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sudah menunggu disini.</i></font>

565
00:42:13,447 --> 00:42:14,649
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak, Ny. Seo.</i></font>

566
00:42:15,182 --> 00:42:16,917
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Biarkan saja pintunya terbuka.</i></font>

567
00:42:16,918 --> 00:42:18,252
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan masuk sekarang.</i></font>

568
00:42:18,386 --> 00:42:20,354
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Baiklah.</font>

569
00:42:23,124 --> 00:42:24,358
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kang Ki Hyung-ssi...,</i></font>

570
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:27,094
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...maaf sekali, ya, soal ini.</i></font>

571
00:42:27,194 --> 00:42:29,964
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kurasa aku harus pergi sekarang.</i></font>

572
00:42:30,531 --> 00:42:33,501
<font color=#FFFF00>Istri cantikmu...</font>

573
00:42:35,436 --> 00:42:37,238
<font color=#FFFF00>...lagi menungguku sekarang.</font>

574
00:42:48,983 --> 00:42:52,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika Reaper akan
menculik Ny. Seo dan Han Byul?</font>

575
00:42:52,145 --> 00:42:55,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Reaper itu tipe orang yang
harus mengendalikan lawannya.</font>

576
00:42:56,023 --> 00:42:59,393
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanya dia membuat Ny. Seo mendatanginya.</font>

577
00:42:59,560 --> 00:43:01,861
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin menunjukkan kekuatannya
pada Kapten Kang.</font>

578
00:43:01,862 --> 00:43:03,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mungkin akan menculik
keluarga Kapten...</font>

579
00:43:03,831 --> 00:43:07,068
<font color=#FFFF00>...ke tempat yang paling secara emosional
akan memengaruhi Kapten Kang.</font>

580
00:43:08,502 --> 00:43:11,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Tempat yang paling secara emosional akan
memengaruhi Kapten Kang...</font>

581
00:43:12,907 --> 00:43:13,908
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu.</font>

582
00:43:15,142 --> 00:43:17,062
<font color=#FFFF00>Tadi Kim Yong
Chul bilang apa di telepon?</font>

583
00:43:17,979 --> 00:43:18,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Pintu.</font>

584
00:43:19,580 --> 00:43:21,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia menyuruhnya
agar pintunya tetap dibiarkan terbuka.</font>

585
00:43:21,549 --> 00:43:22,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Rumah.</font>

586
00:43:23,084 --> 00:43:24,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Rumahnya Kapten Kang.</font>

587
00:43:25,453 --> 00:43:26,554
<font color=#FFFF00>Reaper...</font>

588
00:43:28,155 --> 00:43:31,058
<font color=#FFFF00>...ingin merampas semua
kepunyaan Kapten Kang.</font>

589
00:43:35,863 --> 00:43:36,864
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapten Kang.</font>

590
00:43:40,234 --> 00:43:41,335
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya?</font>

591
00:43:41,736 --> 00:43:44,171
<font color=#FFFF00>Reaper tengah
menuju ke rumah Anda.</font>

592
00:43:46,140 --> 00:43:47,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu.</font>

593
00:43:48,609 --> 00:43:49,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapten Kang.</font>

594
00:43:50,411 --> 00:43:52,013
<font color=#FFFF00>Reaper akan menghubungi Anda.</font>

595
00:43:54,115 --> 00:43:56,050
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Agen Kim Sang Soo]</i></font>

596
00:44:00,087 --> 00:44:01,088
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ki Hyung-ssi...,</i></font>

597
00:44:01,922 --> 00:44:03,391
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...kau baik-baik saja?</i></font>

598
00:44:04,425 --> 00:44:05,426
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.</font>

599
00:44:06,027 --> 00:44:07,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku baik-baik saja.</font>

600
00:44:10,698 --> 00:44:11,699
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tapi kenapa...</i></font>

601
00:44:12,199 --> 00:44:13,901
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dibilang
agen baru itu...</font>

602
00:44:22,677 --> 00:44:23,978
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ki Hyung-ssi.</i></font>

603
00:44:24,745 --> 00:44:25,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won...,</font>

604
00:44:27,148 --> 00:44:30,284
<font color=#FFFF00>...Kim Yong Chul lagi mendengar
panggilan telepon kita ini, 'kan?</font>

605
00:44:30,618 --> 00:44:31,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

606
00:44:33,054 --> 00:44:34,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

607
00:44:34,822 --> 00:44:36,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena aku langsung
mempercayainya.</font>

608
00:44:36,991 --> 00:44:38,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won...,</font>

609
00:44:38,893 --> 00:44:40,194
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tahu panggilan
telepon ini pasti kedengaran...,</font>

610
00:44:41,829 --> 00:44:43,197
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi jangan biarkan dia melihatmu...</font>

611
00:44:44,832 --> 00:44:46,634
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjadi lemah atau
ketakutan.</font>

612
00:44:48,102 --> 00:44:49,203
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Baiklah.</i></font>

613
00:44:49,437 --> 00:44:50,738
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jangan takut, Hae Won.</i></font>

614
00:44:51,605 --> 00:44:53,074
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa Kang Ki Hyung...</i></font>

615
00:44:53,607 --> 00:44:55,976
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada cerita soal kesepakatannya denganku?</font>

616
00:44:57,278 --> 00:44:58,646
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kesepakatan?</i></font>

617
00:44:59,213 --> 00:45:00,373
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jangan dengar dia, Hae Won.</i></font>

618
00:45:01,182 --> 00:45:02,816
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia itu hanya berusaha
membuatmu marah.</font>

619
00:45:02,817 --> 00:45:05,786
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanya itu, kau seharusnya
cerita ke istrimu!</font>

620
00:45:06,954 --> 00:45:09,824
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, maaf, maaf.</font>

621
00:45:11,225 --> 00:45:13,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena rasa gengsimu itu...,</font>

622
00:45:14,662 --> 00:45:17,531
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...Hae Won cantikmu akan segera mati...,</i></font>

623
00:45:18,365 --> 00:45:20,401
<font color=#FFFF00>...begitu juga dengan
anakmu ini.</font>

624
00:45:21,769 --> 00:45:23,703
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa maksud orang ini?</i></font>

625
00:45:23,704 --> 00:45:24,838
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Abaikan dia.</i></font>

626
00:45:24,839 --> 00:45:26,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Abaikan dia, Hae Won.
Jangan dengarkan dia.</font>

627
00:45:27,274 --> 00:45:28,542
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku percaya kau.</font>

628
00:45:29,376 --> 00:45:30,644
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mempercayaimu.</font>

629
00:45:33,114 --> 00:45:34,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won...,</font>

630
00:45:37,952 --> 00:45:39,253
<font color=#FFFF00>...di sebelahmu ada Han Byul, 'kan?</font>

631
00:45:40,187 --> 00:45:41,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Bilang ini ke dia.</font>

632
00:45:41,989 --> 00:45:46,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat butuh bantuan Han Byul
dalam kasus ini.</font>

633
00:45:47,928 --> 00:45:50,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Byul, kau dengar itu?</font>

634
00:45:50,631 --> 00:45:53,134
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari. Kau harus
sapa ayahmu.</font>

635
00:45:57,238 --> 00:45:58,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, hai.</font>

636
00:46:03,511 --> 00:46:04,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai, Han Byul.</font>

637
00:46:05,346 --> 00:46:06,413
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

638
00:46:06,914 --> 00:46:09,216
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa teman Ayah ini
orang jahat?</font>

639
00:46:13,587 --> 00:46:16,123
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Han Byul.</font>

640
00:46:18,159 --> 00:46:19,226
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengar baik-baik.</font>

641
00:46:20,394 --> 00:46:23,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Mulai sekarang, Han Byul,
kita harus sama-sama...</font>

642
00:46:24,598 --> 00:46:26,291
<font color=#FFFF00>...menuntaskan kasus ini.</font>

643
00:46:26,867 --> 00:46:30,271
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah sangat butuh
bantuanmu.</font>

644
00:46:31,405 --> 00:46:34,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau paham perkataan Ayah, 'kan?</font>

645
00:46:34,675 --> 00:46:37,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Ayah, jangan khawatir.</font>

646
00:46:38,279 --> 00:46:39,346
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Han Byul.</i></font>

647
00:46:40,614 --> 00:46:41,816
<font color=#FFFF00>Demi Ayah...</font>

648
00:46:44,718 --> 00:46:46,053
<font color=#FFFF00>...bisa kau peluk ibumu...</font>

649
00:46:48,255 --> 00:46:50,491
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...erat-erat?</i></font>

650
00:47:06,307 --> 00:47:07,308
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu...</font>

651
00:47:09,076 --> 00:47:11,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu betapa Ibu
menyayangimu, 'kan?</font>

652
00:47:15,282 --> 00:47:16,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ibu.</i></font>

653
00:47:26,660 --> 00:47:28,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Byul, mulai.</font>

654
00:47:28,996 --> 00:47:31,765
<font color=#FFFF00>Tik tok, tik tok.</font>

655
00:47:33,200 --> 00:47:35,436
<font color=#FFFF00>Bu, aku harus pergi sekarang.</font>

656
00:47:35,603 --> 00:47:38,072
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mau menyelidiki
kasus sama Ayah.</font>

657
00:47:49,350 --> 00:47:50,918
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Manis sekali anak ini.</i></font>

658
00:47:53,354 --> 00:47:56,757
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takkan sakit menyakitinya,
Detektif Kang Han Byul.</font>

659
00:48:00,895 --> 00:48:02,997
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sayang, Ki Hyung-ssi.</i></font>

660
00:48:04,164 --> 00:48:05,532
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau datang menyelamatkanku, 'kan?</i></font>

661
00:48:06,567 --> 00:48:08,402
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku takut sekali, Ki Hyung-ssi.</i></font>

662
00:48:17,011 --> 00:48:18,112
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hae Won...,</i></font>

663
00:48:19,480 --> 00:48:20,714
<font color=#FFFF00>...maafkan aku.</font>

664
00:48:21,215 --> 00:48:24,084
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak perlu. Kau tak
perlu minta maaf.</font>

665
00:48:25,686 --> 00:48:27,942
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat bahagia
bisa bersamamu selama ini.</font>

666
00:48:27,942 --> 00:48:28,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sudah lebih
dari cukup bagiku.</font>

667
00:48:29,757 --> 00:48:31,091
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Byul juga begitu.</font>

668
00:48:31,425 --> 00:48:34,762
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak perlu minta
maaf padaku.</font>

669
00:48:41,535 --> 00:48:42,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Sayang...,</font>

670
00:48:44,004 --> 00:48:45,005
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...aku...</i></font>

671
00:48:46,173 --> 00:48:48,275
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...padahal aku ingin melihatmu
untuk yang terakhir kalinya.</i></font>

672
00:48:49,176 --> 00:48:50,344
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi sepertinya tak bisa, 'kan?</font>

673
00:48:52,146 --> 00:48:55,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi tolong sampaikan ke Han Byul...</font>

674
00:48:57,017 --> 00:48:59,119
<font color=#FFFF00>...kalau aku tidak akan
meninggalkannya sendirian.</font>

675
00:49:01,622 --> 00:49:02,723
<font color=#FFFF00>Berjanjilah.</font>

676
00:49:03,390 --> 00:49:04,758
<font color=#FFFF00>Berjanjilah padaku</font>

677
00:49:05,826 --> 00:49:07,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku janji, Hae Won.</font>

678
00:49:07,895 --> 00:49:09,163
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku janji.</font>

679
00:51:29,470 --> 00:51:31,004
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sungguh akan membunuhmu...</font>

680
00:51:31,672 --> 00:51:35,142
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menemukan anakmu.</font>

681
00:51:36,510 --> 00:51:38,612
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menunjukkan padanya
bagaimana orang tuanya meninggal...</font>

682
00:51:39,246 --> 00:51:44,435
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan mengatakan padanya
kalau semua itu salah anakmu.</font>

683
00:51:45,519 --> 00:51:46,854
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan setelah itu...</font>

684
00:52:15,849 --> 00:52:16,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Mati.</font>

685
00:52:20,954 --> 00:52:21,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Mati.</font>

686
00:52:23,290 --> 00:52:24,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Mati kau.</font>

687
00:52:25,692 --> 00:52:26,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapten Kang.</font>

688
00:52:28,595 --> 00:52:31,331
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau terpengaruh oleh orang-orang
yang tidak layak hidup..,</font>

689
00:52:32,099 --> 00:52:33,834
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita sama saja
dengan orang itu sendiri.</font>

690
00:52:52,519 --> 00:52:53,787
<font color=#FFFF00>Tembak aku.</font>

691
00:52:55,355 --> 00:52:56,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Tembak saja.</font>

692
00:53:20,847 --> 00:53:22,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa disini?</font>

693
00:53:22,482 --> 00:53:24,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menyelidiki kasus
biar bisa seperti Ayah.</font>

694
00:53:25,052 --> 00:53:26,186
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti polisi.</font>

695
00:53:26,286 --> 00:53:30,157
<font color=#FFFF00>Kang Han Byul, terima kasih telah
menyelidiki kasus ini bersamaku.</font>

696
00:53:30,724 --> 00:53:33,126
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah pasti akan selalu
butuh bantuanmu.</font>

697
00:54:02,389 --> 00:54:07,366
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menyelidiki kasus ini
sesuai perkataan Ayah.</font>

698
00:54:09,196 --> 00:54:10,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Baguslah.</font>

699
00:54:12,499 --> 00:54:14,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagus sekali, Kang Han Byul.</font>

700
00:54:15,068 --> 00:54:16,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kerja bagus.</font>

701
00:54:33,954 --> 00:54:36,056
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Byul, kau baik-baik saja?</font>

702
00:55:28,842 --> 00:55:30,377
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won.</font>

703
00:55:31,111 --> 00:55:32,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won.</font>

704
00:55:34,214 --> 00:55:36,483
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won.</font>

705
00:55:37,050 --> 00:55:38,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Won.</font>

706
00:56:07,914 --> 00:56:09,349
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"Jika iblis memang tidak ada...,"</i></font>

707
00:56:09,349 --> 00:56:12,652
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"...namun manusia yang
telah menciptakannya...,"</i></font>

708
00:56:12,886 --> 00:56:16,187
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"...maka dia telah menciptakan iblis
menurut gambar dan rupanya sendiri."</i></font>

709
00:56:16,189 --> 00:56:17,491
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Fyodor Dostoyevsky.</i></font>

710
00:58:23,683 --> 00:58:25,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Tanpa aku,
kau bisa hidup bagaimana?</font>

711
00:58:25,819 --> 00:58:27,854
<font color=#FFFF00>Pakai dasi sendiri saja, tak bisa.</font>

712
00:59:03,924 --> 00:59:05,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan kembali.</font>

